  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Budujanaperamuna meets the President",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Presidential sources said that arrangements have been made for this meeting to be held at the Presidential Palace.",
        "Finally, in the meeting held between the Parliamentary Committee of the Public Jana Peramuna and the President, President Gotabaya did not make any official response even though many people insisted that there should be a change in the post of Prime Minister.",
        "In this situation, Budujanaperamuna secretary Sagara Kariyawasam said that the president expressed his cowardice in the tone that all political problems can be solved by going to a general election soon.",
        "In such a background, an important member of the party said that even during the meeting with the President to be held tomorrow, the Prime Minister will make strong assertions about the change."
      ],
